Package io.atlasmap.spi

Interface AtlasFieldReader

All Known Implementing Classes:
CsvFieldReader, JavaFieldReader, JsonFieldReader, KafkaConnectFieldReader, XmlFieldReader
public interface AtlasFieldReader
AtlasFieldReader reads the field value from source document. Each format specific module implement its own field reader.
